<h3 id="currently">Currently</h3>
<p>Graduate Research Assistant at Georgia Institute of Technology &amp; Emory University  (BME)</p>

<h3 id="research-interests">Research interests</h3>
<p>Modeling and analysis of neural systems, designing and characterizing control algorithms for the brain.</p>

<hr style="border: 1px dashed #C0C0C0;" />

